title: What causes Obesity in Kiribati
summary: The causes of Obesity in Kiribati are charted above to show that the predominant Cause of Obesity was found to be Genetic at 40.1 percentage .
Fast_Food was the lowest charted percentage at 24.3 percentage with Lack_of_Exercise of only contributing 35 percentage towards the outcome .
